name: Gift Wrap
description:
Please select this option if you would like Little Boogaweezin to gift wrap your item(s) in black tissue paper sealed with an LB sticker along with a personalized hand written note on LB stationary.

Once your order is complete you will need to email us at orders.littleboogaweezin@gmail.com with GIFT WRAP in the subject line. Please include the following information in your email:

1. your order # + your name
2. your personalized message
3. your packages shipping address
